children.text: import { Avatar, Grid, Menu, MenuItem, Typography } from '@material-ui/core';

card: {
        backgroundColor: theme.palette.secondary.dark,
        color: '#fff',
        overflow: 'hidden',
        position: 'relative',
        '&:after': {
            content: '""',
            position: 'absolute',
            width: '210px',
            height: '210px',
            background: theme.palette.secondary[800],
            borderRadius: '50%',
            top: '-85px',
            right: '-95px',
            [theme.breakpoints.down('xs')]: {
                top: '-105px',
                right: '-140px'
            }
        },
        '&:before': {
            content: '""',
            position: 'absolute',
            width: '210px',
            height: '210px',
            background: theme.palette.secondary[800],
            borderRadius: '50%',
            top: '-125px',
            right: '-15px',
            opacity: 0.5,
            [theme.breakpoints.down('xs')]: {
                top: '-155px',
                right: '-70px'
            }
        }
    }
